# Function to post GraphQL query
post_query() {
    local query="$1"
    local variables="$2"
    local data='{"query": "'"$query"'"}'
    if [ ! -z "$variables" ]; then
        data='{"query": "'"$query"'", "variables": '"$variables"'}'
    fi
    response=$(curl -s -X POST -H "Content-Type: application/json" https://api.linear.app/graphql --data "$data")
    echo "$response"
}

# Get John Doe ID
user_query='query GetUser { users(filter: {name: {eq: "John Doe"}}) { nodes { id } } }'
data=$(post_query "$user_query")
john_id=$(echo "$data" | jq -r '.data.users.nodes[0].id' 2>/dev/null)
if [ -z "$john_id" ]; then
    echo "Failed to get John ID: $data"
    exit 1
fi

# Get Engineering team ID
team_query='query GetTeam { teams(filter: {name: {eq: "Engineering"}}) { nodes { id } } }'
data=$(post_query "$team_query")
team_id=$(echo "$data" | jq -r '.data.teams.nodes[0].id' 2>/dev/null)
if [ -z "$team_id" ]; then
    echo "Failed to get team ID: $data"
    exit 1
fi

# Get the issue
issue_query='query GetIssue($teamId: String!, $assigneeId: String!) { team(id: $teamId) { issues(filter: { assignee: {id: {eq: $assigneeId}}, title: {containsIgnoreCase: "login issue"} }) { nodes { id title labels { nodes { id } } } } } }'
variables='{"teamId": "'"$team_id"'", "assigneeId": "'"$john_id"'"}'
data=$(post_query "$issue_query" "$variables")
issues=$(echo "$data" | jq '.data.team.issues.nodes' 2>/dev/null)
if [ "$issues" = "[]" ] || [ -z "$issues" ]; then
    echo "No issue found: $data"
    exit 1
fi
issue_id=$(echo "$issues" | jq -r '.[0].id')
current_label_ids=$(echo "$issues" | jq -r '.[0].labels.nodes[].id' | tr '\n' ' ' | sed 's/ /","/g' | sed 's/,$//')
# For array, better to build it

# Get Bugs label ID
label_query='query GetLabel { issueLabels(first: 1, filter: {name: {eq: "Bugs"}}, orderBy: [{field: "createdAt", direction: DESC}]) { nodes { id } } }'
data=$(post_query "$label_query")
bugs_id=$(echo "$data" | jq -r '.data.issueLabels.nodes[0].id' 2>/dev/null)
if [ -z "$bugs_id" ]; then
    echo "Failed to get Bugs ID: $data"
    exit 1
fi

# Build new label ids
new_label_ids='["'"$bugs_id"'"]'
if [ ! -z "$current_label_ids" ]; then
    if [[ ! "$current_label_ids" =~ "$bugs_id" ]]; then
        new_label_ids='["'"$current_label_ids"'","'"$bugs_id"'"]'  # Wait, current is comma separated
        # Fix: current_label_ids is "id1","id2"
        if [ ! -z "$current_label_ids" ]; then
            new_label_ids='["'"$current_label_ids"'","'"$bugs_id"'"]'
        else
            new_label_ids='["'"$bugs_id"'"]'
        fi
    else
        new_label_ids='["'"$current_label_ids"'"]'
    fi
else
    new_label_ids='["'"$bugs_id"'"]'
fi

# Update issue
update_mutation='mutation UpdateIssue($issueId: String!, $labelIds: [String!]!) { issueUpdate(id: $issueId, input: {labelIds: $labelIds}) { success } }'
variables='{"issueId": "'"$issue_id"'", "labelIds": '"$new_label_ids"'}'
data=$(post_query "$update_mutation" "$variables")
success=$(echo "$data" | jq '.data.issueUpdate.success' 2>/dev/null)
if [ "$success" = "true" ]; then
    echo "Label added successfully"
else
    echo "Failed to add label: $data"
fi
